M140 S90 ; set bed temp
M190 S90 ; wait for bed temp
M109 S240 ; wait for extruder temp
G28 W ; home all without mesh bed level
G80 X110.961 Y90.3609 W28.0781 H29.2781 ; mesh bed levelling

